lead_paragraph: Kris Bryant hit a two-run homer, Jon Lester threw seven scoreless innings and Hector Rondon and Aroldis Chapman completed the shutout to give the Chicago Cubs a 2-0 win over the Houston Astros on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Bryant, Lester Help Cubs Over Astros 2-0
